summary: SHAZAM!: THE WORLD’S MIGHTIEST MORTAL VOL. 1 HC written by DENNIS O’NEIL, OTTO BINDER, ELLIOT S. MAGGIN, E. NELSON BRIDWELL and...
caption:
SHAZAM!: THE WORLD’S MIGHTIEST MORTAL VOL. 1 HC

written by DENNIS O’NEIL, OTTO BINDER, ELLIOT S. MAGGIN, E. NELSON BRIDWELL and others
art by C.C. BECK, KURT SCHAFFENBERGER, DAVE COCKRUM, BOB OKSNER and others
cover by MICHAEL CHO
The 1970s adventures of Shazam—now the star of his very own movie—are collected in color for the first time! These new adventures combined the cartoony art of C.C. Beck, the original artist from the best-selling comics of the 1940s, with the modern, tongue-in-cheek sensibility of writers including Dennis O’Neil as the entire Marvel family reunite for all-new adventures. Collects SHAZAM! #1-18.
ON SALE 05.29.19
$49.99 US | 336 PAGES
FC | ISBN: 978-1-4012-8839-6

summary: Captain Marvel: un nuovo spot potrebbe aver mostrato Monica Rambeau
title: Captain Marvel: un nuovo spot potrebbe aver mostrato Monica Rambeau
body:
Captain Marvel: un nuovo spot potrebbe aver mostrato Monica Rambeau

Un nuovo spot televisivo per Captain Marvel potrebbe aver rivelato una giovane Monica Rambeau.

La maggior parte dello spot televisivo presenta filmati precedentemente pubblicati, ma uno dei momenti inediti mostra Carol Danvers che interagisce con una ragazza che potrebbe essere Monica Rambeau, uno dei personaggi che ha assunto il ruolo di Captain Marvel nei fumetti.

Il momento sembra avvenire…

summary: Y'all the new Captain Marvel TV spot is so rad! We get to see more of Carol being her hilarious and awesome self. She asks...
body: Y'all the new Captain Marvel TV spot is so rad! We get to see more of Carol being her hilarious and awesome self. She asks little Monica how she looked and Monica goes, “Fresh!” and they high five. Carol and Fury fist bump and yell victoriously in a new flight sequence. Maria tells Carol, “It’s time to show these boys how we do it!” Carol smiles and jokes and hollers. I’m so ready and I love it!

title: New Captain Marvel TV Spot Reveals New Footage
body:
New Captain Marvel TV Spot Reveals New Footage

Last night on the Disney Channel, Marvel revealed a brand new Captain Marvel TV spot that features a good amount of new footage.

The spot shows Carol in her red and blue costume interacting with Monica, and something that will make people on the internet pretty mad. All of those people who have been saying the movie would “flop” because Captain Marvel didn’t smile in the previous trailers…
